These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: zinnia, orchid, amaryllis, poppy
There are 4 different nationalities: malaysian, indonesian, australian, pakistani
1. the person who growsorchid is between the person who growszinnia and the indonesian##2
2. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the malaysian##3
3. the person who growsorchid is somewhere between the person who growspoppy and the person who growszinnia##7
4. the indonesian is in an even position##4
5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the australian##1
6. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the malaysian##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Flower   | amaryllis | poppy       | orchid | zinnia        |
| Nationality      | australian  | indonesian | pakistani        | malaysian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, apricot, radish, lemon
House: cottage, farmhouse, palace, tower
1. the tower house is somewhere between the palace house and the person eating radish##7
2. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the left of the person eating artichoke##5
3. the person eating lemon is somewhere to the right of the tower house##5
4. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person eating lemon##1
5. the tower house is between the palace house and the farmhouse house##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Food     | radish | apricot       | lemon         | artichoke     |
| House   | farmhouse   | tower | palace | cottage |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, billiard, domino, backgammon
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: daisy, daffodil, tulip, dahlia
1. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the person who growsdahlia##1
2. the person who growsdahlia is somewhere between the person who growsdaffodil and the person who growsdaisy##7
3. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is somewhere between the person who growsdahlia and the person playing billiard##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Game   | billiard | backgammon | domino | mah-jongg  |
| Flower   | tulip | daisy  | dahlia   | daffodil |

