.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk, almond-milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, october, march, december
1. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person drinking cola is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in october and the person drinking almond-milk##7
3. the person drinking milk is the person who's birthday is in december##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | fanta | cola | almond-milk       | milk |
| Birthday   | october      | august   | march | december  |

