.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, ice-hockey, badminton, volleyball
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, swisher, davidoff, dannemann
1. the dannemann-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##3
2. the tiparillo-smoker is somewhere to the left of the swisher-smoker##5
3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is badminton##1
4. the dannemann-smoker is somewhere between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is sailing##7
5. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the davidoff-smoker##1
6. the swisher-smoker is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Sport         | badminton | sailing   | volleyball | ice-hockey |
| Cigar   | tiparillo      | swisher | dannemann      | davidoff |

