.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: epic, family, martial-arts, disaster
House: tower, victorian, townhouse, craftsman
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the townhouse house##1
2. the townhouse house is the person watching disaster movies##1
3. the victorian house is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
5. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the craftsman house##3
6. the craftsman house is somewhere between the tower house and the victorian house##7
7. the townhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Movie-Genre      | family | epic      | martial-arts | disaster     |
| House   | tower    | craftsman | victorian   | townhouse |

