.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
House: modern, cape-cod, ranch-style, art-deco
4 different games are played: scrabble, billiard, snooker, monopoly
1. the cape-cod house is not the person playing monopoly##6
2. the person playing snooker is on the left or right of the person playing monopoly##3
3. the art-deco house is the person playing snooker##1
4. the ranch-style house is somewhere between the art-deco house and the modern house##7
5. the cape-cod house is on the left of the modern house##1
6. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
7. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| House   | art-deco | ranch-style | cape-cod | modern |
| Game           | snooker   | monopoly    | scrabble       | billiard  |

