4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, old-henry, oliveros, alhambra
1. the person driving the car is not the blend-smoker##6
2. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the car##1
3. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the car##3
4. the person driving the car is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
5. the person driving the tram is somewhere between the alhambra-smoker and the person driving the airplane##7
6. the old-henry-smoker is somewhere to the right of the oliveros-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Transport           | boat | car | tram | airplane |
| Cigar   | alhambra         | oliveros      | blend | old-henry            |

