.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, boat, quad-bike, jet-ski
City: marseilles, paris, new-york, colone
1. the person traveling to colone is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##5
2. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
3. the person traveling to paris is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1
5. the person driving the taxi is between the person driving the boat and the person traveling to paris##2
6. the person traveling to new-york is somewhere between the person traveling to paris and the person driving the boat##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Transport   | jet-ski | taxi | boat | quad-bike   |
| City   | paris    | new-york      | marseilles      | colone |

