2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in november##1
3. the fan techno is not the person who's birthday is in november##6
4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the fan trance##1
5. the fan blues is somewhere to the right of the fan funk##5
6. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere between the person who's birthday is in november and the person who's birthday is in may##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | may | august | september | november |
| Music-Genre   | techno  | trance    | funk    | blues  |

