4. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
5. the videographer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
6. the videographer is on the left of the person who's sport is surfing##1
7. the social-worker is the person who's sport is water-polo##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
