.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, documentary, spy, action
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, parkour, weightlifting, sailing
1. the person watching spy movies is somewhere between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person watching documentary movies##7
2. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person watching spy movies##5
5. the person watching spy movies is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Movie-Genre         | documentary    | spy | action     | crime |
| Sport   | weightlifting | sailing  | parkour | water-polo |

 